Ene Edet otudor otobong dị na July 18,1986 na Douala bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ Cameroon nke na-agba ugbu a maka klọb Kucuk kaymakl nke ugwu Cypriot.
Na 1 Jenụwarị 2010 ọ nọ na ikpe na Ismaily SC na Egypt
O nwere nnwale gara nke ọma mana ọ pụghị ịbịanye aka n'ihi na klọb ya Al-Ittihad enweghị ike iru nkwekọrịta na Ismaily SC na ụgwọ mbufe nke $ 120,000. Ọ laghachiri Al-Ittihad na 13 Jenụwarị 2010

N'ụbọchị nke 10 n'ọnwa Juun afọ 2011, Otobong agafeela Al-Hilal nke Sudan. Na 7 June 2012 Al Hilal tọhapụrụ ya. Na ngwụcha Jenụwarị 2014, ọ hapụrụ otu Moroccan Kawkab Marrakech gaa n'otu Egypt Premier League Misr El-Makasa, na-etinye aka na nkwekọrịta otu afọ na ọkara.
Na ngwụcha Jenụwarị 2016, ọ hapụrụ otu Egypt Misr El-Makasa maka otu KTFF Süper Lig Küçük Kaymaklı Türk S.K., na-etinye aka na nkwekọrịta ọkara afọ.
O gosiputara na Cameroon U-23 na egwuregwu niile nke Africa.
